    "originContent": "> I’m using my personal Apple developer account so I can’t notarize the app with Apple. If you try to install from the GitHub releases page MacOS will warn that it can’t verify the developer identity, so you will need to approve the install on Settings > Privacy, or build from source.",
    "translatedContent": "> 我使用的是个人 Apple 开发者账号，因此无法通过 Apple 进行应用公证。如果你尝试从 GitHub 发布页面安装，MacOS 会提示无法验证开发者身份，你需要在“设置 > 隐私”中批准安装，或者从源码构建。"
